<item>
<title>研究显示AI编程代理能找到正确文件，但会遗漏关键代码行</title>
<link>https://the-decoder.com/ai-coding-agents-find-the-right-file-but-miss-the-exact-lines-that-matter-study-shows/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=36619</guid>
<pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 08:54:47 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】像Claude Code或Codex这样的AI编程代理能可靠地找到正确文件，但会遗漏其中大部分关键代码行。新的SWE-Explore基准测试首次将代码搜索与实际修复分开评估，结果显示，若缺乏足够上下文，即使最佳修复方案也会失败。本文《AI coding agents find the right file but miss the exact lines that matter, study shows》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/ai-coding-agents-find-the-right-file-but-miss-the-exact-lines-that-matter-study-shows/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
